{"tid":1895392,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本三毛 開始出動維穩","createTime":"2020-02-24T13:30:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T18:01:36.000Z","uid":134071,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e76a9f9924aec9a4cc7291d799052427eca10e12","tid":1895392,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T13:30:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1582550506.A.0D5.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1582550506.A.0D5.html&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwfRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=80342b3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1582550506.A.0D5.html</a><br />\n<br />\n作者xxLolaxx (Lola)<br />\n看板Gossiping<br />\n標題[爆卦] 日本網軍開始動作了<br />\n時間Mon Feb 24 21:21:43 2020<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來自日本朋友的爆掛<br />\n<a href=\"https://tinyurl.com/slmmz4r\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2Fslmmz4r&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwfRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=ba384313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tinyurl.com/slmmz4r</a><br />\n<br />\n日本推特同時出現大量轉推<br />\n「｢よく考えたらコロナウイルスかかってる人あんまりいないよね笑｣<br />\n<br />\n仔細想想根本沒有什麼人被感染武漢肺炎嘛（笑）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後就有日本鄉民去搜索了一下....<br />\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/a/tPK6ohG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fa%2FtPK6ohG&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwfRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=33ba69c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://imgur.com/a/tPK6ohG</a><br />\n<br />\n我簡單翻譯日本鄉民的評論<br />\n<br />\n「發現了複數帳號，進階查詢各個帳號的timeline後<br />\n發現都是同樣轉推同樣內容同樣飲料（星巴克的草莓飲料）<br />\n而且各個帳號也都不少follower」<br />\n<br />\n「我查了發現大約有一萬個工作帳號左右...整個不寒而慄」<br />\n<br />\n「因為最近武漢肺炎討論度過熱<br />\n政權批判的很慘，為了壓下這些反對的言論才出動這些網軍<br />\n這就是現階段日本政權的樣貌！」"},{"pid":"dda0897c041d5a82515527065bd26020b2010011","tid":1895392,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T13:30:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23cfe8c30cc8b994a2dbc8003337fde1d92047bd","tid":1895392,"uid":2507,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T13:32:46.000Z","msg":"日本五円"},{"pid":"805ab2290532424505af21805ac176a55f56e786","tid":1895392,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23cfe8c30cc8b994a2dbc8003337fde1d92047bd","tid":1895392,"uid":2507,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T13:32:46.000Z","msg":"日本五円"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T13:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68eed485e02b5971d6c57a2b3ee1cc50983155c2","tid":1895392,"uid":18279,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T13:33:30.000Z","msg":"天佑日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc3540c7e8957755d7b1724bb199eddd736de1e","tid":1895392,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68eed485e02b5971d6c57a2b3ee1cc50983155c2","tid":1895392,"uid":18279,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T13:33:30.000Z","msg":"天佑日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T13:34:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55192f3d71dd9c611c2c2c3dc3604cbb638afd3","tid":1895392,"uid":191812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"23cfe8c30cc8b994a2dbc8003337fde1d92047bd","tid":1895392,"uid":2507,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T13:32:46.000Z","msg":"日本五円"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020